ASH-thetics
Find your aesthetics here.

ASH-thetics is a curated aesthetic shopping and room inspiration website for students, young adults, and anyone who wants a beautiful space on a budget. It brings together cozy decor, desk setup finds, bedroom pieces, wall accents, and budget-friendly Amazon picks in one visual browsing experience.

Live Site
https://ash-thetics.vercel.app

What It Does
Showcases aesthetic home decor and lifestyle finds
Organizes products by categories like cozy lighting, bedroom decor, desk setup, wall decor, under-budget finds, and premium picks
Links visitors directly to Amazon product pages
Shares room inspiration and curated visual ideas
Includes a newsletter section for weekly aesthetic finds
Built With
HTML
CSS
JavaScript
Vercel for deployment
Project Goal
The goal of ASH-thetics is to make aesthetic room styling easier and more affordable. Instead of searching through endless product pages, visitors can quickly discover items that match a clean, cozy, minimal, or dreamy room aesthetic.

Current Features
Responsive landing page
Product cards with images and links
Category-based browsing
Inspiration sections
Amazon affiliate-style product links
Newsletter signup section
Planned Improvements
Add more curated product collections
Improve mobile performance
Add search and filtering
Create separate pages for each aesthetic
Add a blog or styling guide section
Add clearer affiliate and privacy information
Repository Structure
ASH-thetics/
├── index.html
└── ash-thetics-final (3).html
index.html is the main website file. The extra HTML file appears to be an earlier or exported version and can be cleaned up once the final version is confirmed.

Affiliate Disclosure
Some product links may be affiliate links. This means ASH-thetics may earn a small commission if a visitor purchases through those links, at no extra cost to them.

